sentences: Su-Elise Michelle Nash (born 22 May 1981) is an English singer who rose to fame in the now-defunct girl group, Mis-Teeq.
In September 2009 it was confirmed that during an interview at the MOBO Awards that Nash was working on her solo debut album entitled Long Way Round, due to be released in 2010.
